N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 441.104 - Emergency outpatient

State Regulations

An emergency outpatient is one who is admitted to the
emergency, accident or equivalent service of the hospital for the diagnosis
and/or treatment of a condition. The service is one operated pursuant to
section
405.1033
of this
subchapter. Notes
